Matrix interfaces and factories holding elements of dcomplex data type.

Interface Summary

Class Summary

DComplexFactory2D Factory for convenient construction of 2-d matrices holding complex cells.
DComplexFactory3D Factory for convenient construction of 3-d matrices holding complex cells.
DComplexMatrix1D Abstract base class for 1-d matrices (aka vectors) holding complex elements.

DComplexMatrix3D Abstract base class for 3-d matrices holding complex elements.
